CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Handsome Pair - Mr. and Mrs. Edward T. Prather following their marriage Nov. 12. The bride is the former Miss Constance Louise Boyd. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Edward T. Prather wearing moustache, light colored bow tie, and light colored carnation on left lapel, standing with smiling Constance Louise Prather (Boyd) wearing headpiece with mid length veil, long sleeved gown with floral lace overlay and crinoline skirt, standing at table with three tiered wedding cake in interior with fireplace, possibly on Dinwiddie Street, Hill District
